Cathars, Druids, Moors, Islam.

00:19:16.550 --> 00:19:19.843 align:middle line:90%
This was a threat to the church.

00:19:19.843 --> 00:19:22.010 align:middle line:84%
I mean, here we are in the
middle of the Inquisition

00:19:22.010 --> 00:19:24.650 align:middle line:84%
at this point, and the church
was hunting down heretics

00:19:24.650 --> 00:19:26.420 align:middle line:90%
all throughout Europe.

00:19:26.420 --> 00:19:29.900 align:middle line:84%
And we have this one
little country of Portugal

00:19:29.900 --> 00:19:32.960 align:middle line:84%
