00:19:38.000 --> 00:19:40.850 align:middle line:84%
>> We also know that the
Templars were rumored to have

00:19:40.850 --> 00:19:44.630 align:middle line:84%
discovered the bloodline
of Jesus and Mary Magdalene

00:19:44.630 --> 00:19:45.995 align:middle line:90%
and protected their descendants.

00:19:45.995 --> 00:19:47.900 align:middle line:90%
[VOCALIZING]

00:19:47.900 --> 00:19:51.740 align:middle line:84%
Silva says in his book that
"Portugal" can actually

00:19:51.740 --> 00:19:56.080 align:middle line:84%
be interpreted as
"port of the grail."

00:19:56.080 --> 00:19:57.910 align:middle line:84%
So how would he
define the meaning

00:19:57.910 --> 00:20:00.610 align:middle line:90%
of the grail in this context?

00:20:00.610 --> 00:20:02.980 align:middle line:10%
>> I was looking
at the king's seal.

00:20:02.980 --> 00:20:05.350 align:middle line:10%
And to all appearances,
the first clue

00:20:05.350 --> 00:20:07.150 align:middle line:10%
that nothing is really
out of the ordinary

00:20:07.150 --> 00:20:10.150 align:middle line:10%
is that your eye glances
over the king's seal,

00:20:10.150 --> 00:20:12.400 align:middle line:10%
and it says Portugal.

00:20:12.400 --> 00:20:14.320 align:middle line:10%
And you think,
OK, it's Portugal.

00:20:14.320 --> 00:20:16.690 align:middle line:10%
But if you're an
initiate of the mysteries

00:20:16.690 --> 00:20:19.930 align:middle line:10%
and you know how to hide
things in plain sight,

00:20:19.930 --> 00:20:22.460 align:middle line:10%
you basically look
at this a bit slower.

00:20:22.460 --> 00:20:25.450 align:middle line:84%
You look at the way that the
letters have been formulated

00:20:25.450 --> 00:20:27.550 align:middle line:90%
over this Templar cross.

00:20:27.550 --> 00:20:31.480 align:middle line:84%
And it literally
reads "portu-gral."

00:20:31.480 --> 00:20:35.110 align:middle line:84%
It's a suggestion that
somehow, the grail is involved

00:20:35.110 --> 00:20:36.640 align:middle line:90%
in Portuguese territory.

00:20:36.640 --> 00:20:37.570 align:middle line:10%
It's very subtle.

00:20:37.570 --> 00:20:39.277 align:middle line:10%
But to anyone who
knows the mysteries,

00:20:39.277 --> 00:20:41.110 align:middle line:10%
they know these subtleties,
and they pick up

00:20:41.110 --> 00:20:43.060 align:middle line:10%
on these little clues.

00:20:43.060 --> 00:20:45.310 align:middle line:84%
But to a person
who's deeply involved

00:20:45.310 --> 00:20:47.980 align:middle line:84%
in metaphor and
symbolism, you begin

00:20:47.980 --> 00:20:50.260 align:middle line:84%
to read the letters
as an anagram.

00:20:50.260 --> 00:20:53.440 align:middle line:84%
And if you're Portuguese,
it reads as a phrase.

00:20:53.440 --> 00:20:56.660 align:middle line:84%
And it says "por tu
o gral," and that

00:20:56.660 --> 00:21:00.770 align:middle line:84%
translates as "through
you, the grail," which

00:21:00.770 --> 00:21:02.840 align:middle line:84%
means there's something
about that territory,

00:21:02.840 --> 00:21:06.410 align:middle line:84%
that town in which Tomar
sits, the Templar stronghold,

00:21:06.410 --> 00:21:10.050 align:middle line:84%
that is associated with
some kind of grail quest,

00:21:10.050 --> 00:21:12.920 align:middle line:84%
some kind of understanding
of what the grail is about

00:21:12.920 --> 00:21:14.300 align:middle line:90%
and what it does to you.

00:21:14.300 --> 00:21:17.930 align:middle line:10%
Because the same phrase is
also found, of all places,

00:21:17.930 --> 00:21:21.800 align:middle line:10%
on the northeastern pillar
of Chartres Cathedral, where

00:21:21.800 --> 00:21:24.140 align:middle line:10%
there's a depiction
of the actual grail

00:21:24.140 --> 00:21:25.370 align:middle line:10%
and the Ark of the Covenant.

00:21:25.370 --> 00:21:29.180 align:middle line:84%
And it says right under there,
"through you, the grail."

00:21:29.180 --> 00:21:31.220 align:middle line:84%
And if we understand
and make the connection

00:21:31.220 --> 00:21:34.700 align:middle line:84%
between what the
Cistercians and the Templars

00:21:34.700 --> 00:21:36.770 align:middle line:84%
were doing in Chartres
Cathedral and what

00:21:36.770 --> 00:21:39.830 align:middle line:84%
they were doing in Tomar in
Portugal, there is an overlap.

00:21:39.830 --> 00:21:42.950 align:middle line:84%
And that is to do
with the mysteries.

00:21:42.950 --> 00:21:44.720 align:middle line:84%
And to understand
the mysteries is

00:21:44.720 --> 00:21:46.940 align:middle line:84%
to understand what the
grail really is about.

00:21:46.940 --> 00:21:50.391 align:middle line:90%


