00:37:35.260 --> 00:37:37.520 align:middle line:90%
and spills the water out.

00:37:37.520 --> 00:37:41.450 align:middle line:84%
That change of weight allows the
hammer to go back down again,

00:37:41.450 --> 00:37:42.830 align:middle line:90%
compacting everything.

00:37:42.830 --> 00:37:47.990 align:middle line:90%


00:37:47.990 --> 00:37:50.510 align:middle line:84%
It was built by
the Captain Moore.

00:37:50.510 --> 00:37:52.970 align:middle line:84%
He had slaves, and
they were the ones

00:37:52.970 --> 00:37:55.520 align:middle line:84%
that built the
[PORTUGUESE] in our town.

00:37:55.520 --> 00:37:57.050 align:middle line:90%
They lived there.

00:37:57.050 --> 00:37:59.840 align:middle line:90%
And here was their pathway.

00:37:59.840 --> 00:38:02.930 align:middle line:84%
They built it there because
there was a lot of water

00:38:02.930 --> 00:38:04.679 align:middle line:90%
to make the mill work.

00:38:04.679 --> 00:38:07.673 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:38:07.673 --> 00:38:09.670 align:middle line:90%


00:38:09.670 --> 00:38:13.900 align:middle line:84%
>> After leaving Brazil in 2015,
Kathleen's life is not only

00:38:13.900 --> 00:38:16.690 align:middle line:84%
filled with much
additional research,

00:38:16.690 --> 00:38:20.350 align:middle line:84%
she also encounters
some serious obstacles.

00:38:20.350 --> 00:38:24.280 align:middle line:84%
For instance, nine days
after she returns to the US,

00:38:24.280 --> 00:38:29.230 align:middle line:84%
Kathleen's home, art studio, and
several personal works of art

00:38:29.230 --> 00:38:33.310 align:middle line:84%
are destroyed in the Butte
Fire of Northern California.

00:38:33.310 --> 00:38:36.760 align:middle line:84%
Only six weeks later, she
is admitted to the hospital

00:38:36.760 --> 00:38:39.040 align:middle line:84%
and undergoes a
liver transplant,

00:38:39.040 --> 00:38:42.430 align:middle line:84%
following a four-year
battle with liver cancer.

00:38:42.430 --> 00:38:44.890 align:middle line:84%
These circumstances,
among others,

00:38:44.890 --> 00:38:48.500 align:middle line:84%
prevent her from returning
to Brazil for two more years.

00:38:48.500 --> 00:38:52.470 align:middle line:90%


00:38:52.470 --> 00:38:54.660 align:middle line:84%
After recuperating
from the surgery

00:38:54.660 --> 00:38:59.160 align:middle line:84%
and having satisfactorily
relocated, in 2017,

00:38:59.160 --> 00:39:03.810 align:middle line:84%
Kathleen sets out to
rediscover the cave in Brazil.

00:39:03.810 --> 00:39:07.800 align:middle line:84%
Unfortunately, her
efforts yield no results.

00:39:07.800 --> 00:39:13.210 align:middle line:84%
A huge fire has struck the
Alto Paraíso area that year.

00:39:13.210 --> 00:39:16.890 align:middle line:84%
The fire, encompassing
several thousand acres,

00:39:16.890 --> 00:39:21.750 align:middle line:84%
has scorched the land
where the cave is located.

00:39:21.750 --> 00:39:24.270 align:middle line:84%
Disappointed but
not discouraged,

00:39:24.270 --> 00:39:27.360 align:middle line:84%
Kathleen makes arrangements
with the caretaker of the land

00:39:27.360 --> 00:39:30.000 align:middle line:90%
to return the following year.

00:39:30.000 --> 00:39:32.490 align:middle line:84%
But while dining
with friends in town,

00:39:32.490 --> 00:39:36.960 align:middle line:84%
she is introduced to a film
director, Trajano Paiva,

00:39:36.960 --> 00:39:39.420 align:middle line:90%
who knows about her project.

00:39:39.420 --> 00:39:43.230 align:middle line:84%
Trajano offers to film the
rediscovery of the cave

00:39:43.230 --> 00:39:44.180 align:middle line:90%
the following year.

00:39:44.180 --> 00:39:47.140 align:middle line:90%


00:39:47.140 --> 00:39:54.040 align:middle line:84%
June 2018, Kathleen returns
once more to Alto Paraíso.

00:39:54.040 --> 00:39:58.060 align:middle line:84%
This place and its distinct
ambience has grown on her.

00:39:58.060 --> 00:40:00.550 align:middle line:10%
She is now quite
attached to its people,

00:40:00.550 --> 00:40:03.790 align:middle line:10%
their laid-back lifestyle,
and the natural beauty

00:40:03.790 --> 00:40:05.860 align:middle line:10%
of their region.

00:40:05.860 --> 00:40:08.540 align:middle line:90%
But there is something more.

00:40:08.540 --> 00:40:13.720 align:middle line:84%
The English translation of Alto
Paraíso is "high paradise."

00:40:13.720 --> 00:40:17.206 align:middle line:90%
[MAJESTIC MUSIC]

00:40:17.206 --> 00:40:23.190 align:middle line:90%


00:40:23.190 --> 00:40:25.950 align:middle line:84%
It is the multicultural,
multireligious,

00:40:25.950 --> 00:40:30.420 align:middle line:84%
and multilingual backgrounds
of the people of Alto Paraíso,

00:40:30.420 --> 00:40:36.300 align:middle line:84%
Sáo Jorge, and Moinho that
make this place so magical.

00:40:36.300 --> 00:40:39.720 align:middle line:84%
People from all corners of
the Earth who visit this area

00:40:39.720 --> 00:40:43.490 align:middle line:84%
find themselves returning
year after year.

00:40:43.490 --> 00:40:45.930 align:middle line:84%
Many choose to make it
their permanent home.

00:40:45.930 --> 00:40:51.050 align:middle line:90%


00:40:51.050 --> 00:40:55.630 align:middle line:84%
So Kathleen asks herself, isn't
this truly the Templars' dream

00:40:55.630 --> 00:40:57.700 align:middle line:90%
become reality?

00:40:57.700 --> 00:41:00.490 align:middle line:84%
Whether inspired by
their intention or not,

00:41:00.490 --> 00:41:04.690 align:middle line:84%
Alto Paraíso and its surrounding
communities are undeniably

00:41:04.690 --> 00:41:09.040 align:middle line:84%
composed of people with diverse
backgrounds and divergent

00:41:09.040 --> 00:41:12.820 align:middle line:84%
experiences who are nevertheless
living in harmony with each

00:41:12.820 --> 00:41:14.290 align:middle line:90%
other.

00:41:14.290 --> 00:41:16.060 align:middle line:84%
There can be no
doubt about that.

00:41:16.060 --> 00:41:22.220 align:middle line:90%


00:41:22.220 --> 00:41:25.220 align:middle line:84%
Kathleen and the film
director, Trajano Paiva,

00:41:25.220 --> 00:41:30.410 align:middle line:84%
procure permission to access the
land where the cave is located.

00:41:30.410 --> 00:41:32.570 align:middle line:84%
They gather up their
gear and set off

00:41:32.570 --> 00:41:34.980 align:middle line:90%
into the vast wilderness.

00:41:34.980 --> 00:41:38.660 align:middle line:84%
They go without a guide but with
a great sense of determination

00:41:38.660 --> 00:41:40.025 align:middle line:90%
to rediscover the cave.

00:41:40.025 --> 00:41:43.220 align:middle line:90%


00:41:43.220 --> 00:41:47.670 align:middle line:84%
However, this turns out to
be a rather difficult task.

00:41:47.670 --> 00:41:51.230 align:middle line:84%
The previous year's fire
has burned all the trails

00:41:51.230 --> 00:41:54.270 align:middle line:84%
and completely
changed the landscape,

00:41:54.270 --> 00:41:58.430 align:middle line:84%
making it almost
entirely unrecognizable.

00:41:58.430 --> 00:42:01.520 align:middle line:84%
The first day out,
Trajano and Kathleen

00:42:01.520 --> 00:42:04.430 align:middle line:84%
give up after
hours of searching.

00:42:04.430 --> 00:42:07.280 align:middle line:84%
They're tired, hungry,
and with no better

00:42:07.280 --> 00:42:09.860 align:middle line:84%
idea of where the cave is
than when they started out.

00:42:09.860 --> 00:42:13.500 align:middle line:90%


00:42:13.500 --> 00:42:16.790 align:middle line:84%
In fact, several more days
pass before they are again

00:42:16.790 --> 00:42:19.280 align:middle line:90%
granted access to the land.

00:42:19.280 --> 00:42:22.850 align:middle line:84%
But this time, they find
an old, rusted sign hidden

00:42:22.850 --> 00:42:25.850 align:middle line:90%
by brush that reads gruta--

00:42:25.850 --> 00:42:28.010 align:middle line:90%
"cave" in English.

00:42:28.010 --> 00:42:31.130 align:middle line:84%
So they at least have
a starting point.

00:42:31.130 --> 00:42:34.940 align:middle line:84%
The sign, and Kathleen's
memory of her 2015 visit,

00:42:34.940 --> 00:42:39.320 align:middle line:84%
give them a general sense
of where the cave should be.

00:42:39.320 --> 00:42:42.500 align:middle line:84%
Once again, Kathleen
and Trajano set out

00:42:42.500 --> 00:42:46.010 align:middle line:84%
with high hopes of
finding the cave.

00:42:46.010 --> 00:42:51.560 align:middle line:84%
Their first three attempts
lead to nothing but dead ends.

00:42:51.560 --> 00:42:54.860 align:middle line:84%
It is only on their last
chance to find the cave

00:42:54.860 --> 00:42:58.730 align:middle line:84%
that Kathleen's intuition
finally bears fruit.

00:42:58.730 --> 00:43:03.590 align:middle line:90%


00:43:03.590 --> 00:43:07.360 align:middle line:84%
Trajano, weighed down with
his heavy film equipment,

00:43:07.360 --> 00:43:09.190 align:middle line:90%
is ready to give up.

00:43:09.190 --> 00:43:12.490 align:middle line:84%
But Kathleen insists
on persevering.

00:43:12.490 --> 00:43:15.640 align:middle line:84%
She makes her way through
dangerously tall grass,

00:43:15.640 --> 00:43:19.030 align:middle line:84%
which hides not only deep
ruts and boulders but also

00:43:19.030 --> 00:43:21.880 align:middle line:90%
poisonous snakes and spiders.

00:43:21.880 --> 00:43:24.970 align:middle line:84%
And she finds the
vein of crystal

00:43:24.970 --> 00:43:28.060 align:middle line:90%
that she last saw in 2015.

00:43:28.060 --> 00:43:33.910 align:middle line:84%
>> It's about three
feet, four feet, deep--

00:43:33.910 --> 00:43:40.780 align:middle line:84%
wide, wide-- and probably about
four to five feet in height.

00:43:40.780 --> 00:43:43.780 align:middle line:84%
And it's solid crystal
all the way down.

00:43:43.780 --> 00:43:45.910 align:middle line:84%
There's a vein of it
that goes all the way

00:43:45.910 --> 00:43:49.870 align:middle line:90%
down this whole area.

00:43:49.870 --> 00:43:52.140 align:middle line:90%
Yeah, all this whole area.

00:43:52.140 --> 00:43:55.102 align:middle line:90%
I will show you a piece.

00:43:55.102 --> 00:43:58.010 align:middle line:90%


00:43:58.010 --> 00:44:00.810 align:middle line:90%
This is what it looks like.

00:44:00.810 --> 00:44:02.716 align:middle line:90%
We have a piece of it.

00:44:02.716 --> 00:44:05.570 align:middle line:90%
It's white crystal.

00:44:05.570 --> 00:44:12.620 align:middle line:84%
And this whole thing, this
whole wall, is all of crystal.

00:44:12.620 --> 00:44:16.492 align:middle line:90%


00:44:16.492 --> 00:44:17.944 align:middle line:90%
It's magnificent.

00:44:17.944 --> 00:44:20.450 align:middle line:84%
And we cross over it
before we get to the cave.

00:44:20.450 --> 00:44:23.620 align:middle line:90%


00:44:23.620 --> 00:44:26.170 align:middle line:84%
>> Now she knows that the
cave is only another mile

00:44:26.170 --> 00:44:28.660 align:middle line:90%
or so farther away.

00:44:28.660 --> 00:44:31.100 align:middle line:90%
But in which direction?

00:44:31.100 --> 00:44:31.900 align:middle line:90%
>> OK.

00:44:31.900 --> 00:44:37.510 align:middle line:84%
So the first time I came, we
crossed this crystal wall,

00:44:37.510 --> 00:44:39.070 align:middle line:84%
and then we went
down to the cave.

00:44:39.070 --> 00:44:41.590 align:middle line:84%
So I'm not sure if
it's this direction

00:44:41.590 --> 00:44:43.340 align:middle line:84%
or if we came in
from this direction.

00:44:43.340 --> 00:44:44.140 align:middle line:90%
I'm not sure.

00:44:44.140 --> 00:44:46.850 align:middle line:90%
We'll have to check both ways.

00:44:46.850 --> 00:44:50.300 align:middle line:84%
I'll have to see
both ways and see.

00:44:50.300 --> 00:44:55.850 align:middle line:84%
So a little bit more exploring
to do before we find the prize.

00:44:55.850 --> 00:44:58.700 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHING]

00:44:58.700 --> 00:45:00.600 align:middle line:84%
We can walk the wall
and look this way

00:45:00.600 --> 00:45:02.630 align:middle line:90%
and look this way, too.

00:45:02.630 --> 00:45:07.880 align:middle line:84%
Walk the wall this way and
then walk the wall this way

00:45:07.880 --> 00:45:11.710 align:middle line:84%
and see which way
where we find the cave.

00:45:11.710 --> 00:45:21.210 align:middle line:90%


00:45:21.210 --> 00:45:23.280 align:middle line:84%
>> Following the vein
of quartz crystal,

00:45:23.280 --> 00:45:26.130 align:middle line:84%
first in one direction
and then the other,

00:45:26.130 --> 00:45:30.200 align:middle line:84%
she notices a knoll off
to the right below them.

00:45:30.200 --> 00:45:35.800 align:middle line:84%
The knoll has an odd, dark
area just in front of it.

00:45:35.800 --> 00:45:39.550 align:middle line:84%
Instinctively, Kathleen
feels that this is it.

00:45:39.550 --> 00:45:42.820 align:middle line:84%
She thinks that they may
have found the cave entrance.

00:45:42.820 --> 00:45:45.070 align:middle line:90%
But Trajano has doubts.

00:45:45.070 --> 00:45:48.040 align:middle line:84%
Perhaps what Kathleen sees
as the mouth of the cave

00:45:48.040 --> 00:45:51.580 align:middle line:84%
is only a shadow created
by the overhanging brush.

00:45:51.580 --> 00:45:55.150 align:middle line:84%
He worries about hiking downhill
with his heavy equipment

00:45:55.150 --> 00:45:58.450 align:middle line:84%
for what may be only
an optical illusion.

00:45:58.450 --> 00:46:01.810 align:middle line:84%
So while Trajano waits,
Kathleen heads down

00:46:01.810 --> 00:46:04.370 align:middle line:90%
to explore on her own.

00:46:04.370 --> 00:46:07.990 align:middle line:84%
The closer she comes,
the surer she is.

00:46:07.990 --> 00:46:12.430 align:middle line:84%
Within 100 yards or so of the
cave, she calls out to Trajano

00:46:12.430 --> 00:46:15.260 align:middle line:84%
and tells him to
bring the equipment.

00:46:15.260 --> 00:46:18.220 align:middle line:84%
He will soon see this
magnificent discovery

00:46:18.220 --> 00:46:20.170 align:middle line:90%
with his own eyes.

00:46:20.170 --> 00:46:24.640 align:middle line:84%
More importantly, he will
document it with his camera.

00:46:24.640 --> 00:46:29.300 align:middle line:84%
Moments later, Kathleen is
just 20 feet from the cave.

00:46:29.300 --> 00:46:31.370 align:middle line:84%
She can see the
edges of the opening

00:46:31.370 --> 00:46:35.690 align:middle line:84%
almost completely overgrown
with bushes and small trees.

00:46:35.690 --> 00:46:39.110 align:middle line:84%
The brush is her only
remaining obstacle now,

00:46:39.110 --> 00:46:42.470 align:middle line:84%
and she immediately
begins to clear it away.

00:46:42.470 --> 00:46:44.526 align:middle line:90%
Until there it is again.

00:46:44.526 --> 00:46:45.458 align:middle line:90%
>> Woo!

00:46:45.458 --> 00:46:48.260 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHS]

00:46:48.260 --> 00:46:51.470 align:middle line:90%
OK, it's easier to walk in here.

00:46:51.470 --> 00:46:52.550 align:middle line:90%
Push down the bushes.

00:46:52.550 --> 00:46:54.250 align:middle line:84%
No one's been here
for a long time.

00:46:54.250 --> 00:46:59.820 align:middle line:90%


00:46:59.820 --> 00:47:02.070 align:middle line:90%
Yeah, there's the cross.

00:47:02.070 --> 00:47:05.100 align:middle line:90%
You see the cross?

00:47:05.100 --> 00:47:08.970 align:middle line:84%
>> The Templar cave, carved
out with nothing more than hand

00:47:08.970 --> 00:47:14.700 align:middle line:84%
tools, sometime
between 1292 and 1315.

00:47:14.700 --> 00:47:19.260 align:middle line:84%
And above it is the
distinctive Templar cross that

00:47:19.260 --> 00:47:21.820 align:middle line:90%
marks it as Templar property.

00:47:21.820 --> 00:47:23.644 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah, I can see it.

00:47:23.644 --> 00:47:24.620 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah, this is it.

00:47:24.620 --> 00:47:26.572 align:middle line:90%
This is the Templar cave.

00:47:26.572 --> 00:47:29.500 align:middle line:90%
Now, there's a Templar cross.

00:47:29.500 --> 00:47:31.940 align:middle line:90%
[PANTING]

00:47:31.940 --> 00:47:33.320 align:middle line:90%


00:47:33.320 --> 00:47:34.120 align:middle line:90%
Woo-hoo!

00:47:34.120 --> 00:47:36.040 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHS]

00:47:36.040 --> 00:47:41.320 align:middle line:90%


00:47:41.320 --> 00:47:45.170 align:middle line:84%
The Templar cross
right here, the same

00:47:45.170 --> 00:47:48.870 align:middle line:84%
cross I saw in Domme,
France, in 1307.

00:47:48.870 --> 00:47:54.080 align:middle line:84%
There was 1307, dated, where
they kept the Templar knights

00:47:54.080 --> 00:47:56.340 align:middle line:90%
in Domme, France in the dungeon.

00:47:56.340 --> 00:48:01.090 align:middle line:84%
And they left graffiti the
same as this, the same tool

00:48:01.090 --> 00:48:02.110 align:middle line:90%
markings.

00:48:02.110 --> 00:48:04.630 align:middle line:90%
This was done by hand tools.

00:48:04.630 --> 00:48:07.570 align:middle line:84%
This was not done
by modern tools--

00:48:07.570 --> 00:48:09.750 align:middle line:90%
hand tools.

00:48:09.750 --> 00:48:13.495 align:middle line:90%
A Templar cross, a Templar cave.

00:48:13.495 --> 00:48:18.305 align:middle line:90%


00:48:18.305 --> 00:48:19.760 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:48:19.760 --> 00:48:23.030 align:middle line:10%
>> In your professional
opinion as a researcher

00:48:23.030 --> 00:48:25.580 align:middle line:10%
of the Templars, I'm going to
show you a picture of a cross

00:48:25.580 --> 00:48:26.850 align:middle line:10%
that we found in Brazil.

00:48:26.850 --> 00:48:30.580 align:middle line:90%


00:48:30.580 --> 00:48:33.220 align:middle line:90%
>> Wow.

00:48:33.220 --> 00:48:36.040 align:middle line:84%
I would say immediately
that it is a cross related

00:48:36.040 --> 00:48:37.180 align:middle line:90%
with the Templars.

00:48:37.180 --> 00:48:39.700 align:middle line:84%
There's no doubt it
has relations with it.

00:48:39.700 --> 00:48:46.440 align:middle line:90%


00:48:46.440 --> 00:48:50.230 align:middle line:84%
>> This strong evidence of the
Templars' presence here in Alto

00:48:50.230 --> 00:48:55.140 align:middle line:84%
Paraíso, Brazil inspires Dr.
Kathleen Ball to continue

00:48:55.140 --> 00:48:58.920 align:middle line:84%
to search the area for more
artifacts and to interview more

00:48:58.920 --> 00:49:01.080 align:middle line:90%
of the local people.

00:49:01.080 --> 00:49:03.630 align:middle line:84%
The information they
provide may help

00:49:03.630 --> 00:49:08.910 align:middle line:84%
her establish and track down
the Templar roots in this area.

00:49:08.910 --> 00:49:11.270 align:middle line:84%
Most of all, the
evidence motivates

00:49:11.270 --> 00:49:14.120 align:middle line:84%
Kathleen to keep
researching and keep

00:49:14.120 --> 00:49:16.850 align:middle line:84%
visiting the lands
of the Templars

00:49:16.850 --> 00:49:21.210 align:middle line:84%
to bring this mysterious
order out of the shadows

00:49:21.210 --> 00:49:26.370 align:middle line:84%
and into the hearts
and minds of all.

00:49:26.370 --> 00:49:28.400 align:middle line:90%
>> I'm going back to Brazil.

00:49:28.400 --> 00:49:31.610 align:middle line:84%
There is much more
to discover there.

00:49:31.610 --> 00:49:33.830 align:middle line:90%
This story is just not finished.

00:49:33.830 --> 00:49:36.230 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:49:36.230 --> 00:50:03.830 align:middle line:90%


00:50:03.830 --> 00:50:07.480 align:middle line:90%
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:50:07.480 --> 00:52:23.000 align:middle line:90%